readme:
Service Usage

This service is used for receiving biometric (face and fingerprint) enrolments for offshore Visa applications from the provider.

Service Behaviour

CSP captures the required data and sends to BAMS to consume using SV398.
BAMS then sends data using SV540 to CDH
CDH then sends data using SV563 to CSP for display.
